com.camerontec.catalys.util.dictionary

Class FIXRepeatingGroupTags

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.util.dictionary.FIXRepeatingGroupTags

  • public class FIXRepeatingGroupTags
extends Object
    This class keeps information about repeated and nested tags for a specific FIX message type and dictionary name. It builds the data from the FIX dictionary.
    See Also:
    IDictionary
